ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「桜？　なんだ？　お前の次回作は桜なのか？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00107",
linknext="block_00109",
},
block_00109={
{"fg",ch="明石",size="z1",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0002",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000753",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「まぁ、いいではないか。とりあえず、万事うまくいったのじゃ。",
{"rt2"},
"これでグッドエンドじゃろ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00108",
linknext="block_00110",
},
block_00110={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「ふっ、お前が言うのなら、そうかもな……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00109",
linknext="block_00111",
},
block_00111={
{"fg",ch="明石",size="z1",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0003",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"fgact",ch="明石",act="うなづく",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000754",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「うむ、それでは、ワシもここでさらばとする」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00110",
linknext="block_00112",
},
block_00112={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「でも、最後に確認するが、金は本当に良かったのか？",
{"rt2"},
"なんとか、フリッドマンから取り返す手だってあるかもしれないんだぞ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00111",
linknext="block_00113",
},
block_00113={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「まぁ、かなり厄介だとは思うけど……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00112",
linknext="block_00114",
},
block_00114={
{"fg",ch="明石",size="z1",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1b0000",face="b0001",head="aka_z1b",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000755",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「なーに、俺みたいなビックな人間には、あんなものはした金だよ。",
{"rt2"},
"いらんもんはいらん」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00113",
linknext="block_00115",
},
block_00115={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「そんな事言って、あとで後悔するぞ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00114",
linknext="block_00116",
},
block_00116={
{"fg",ch="明石",size="z1",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1b0000",face="b0002",head="aka_z1b",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000756",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「それは、お前もだろ？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00115",
linknext="block_00117",
},
block_00117={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「かもな……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00116",
linknext="block_00118",
},
block_00118={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"二人は大金を目の前にしながら、一銭も手に入れる事は出来なかった。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00117",
linknext="block_00119",
},
block_00119={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"だが、この二人は、根っからのバカなので、逆に一銭も残らない方がすがすがしい。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00118",
linknext="block_00120",
},
block_00120={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"まぁ、あとで後悔したりもするんだろうけどさ……。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00119",
linknext="block_00121",
},
block_00121={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「お互いバカだな」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00120",
linknext="block_00122",
},
block_00122={
{"fg",ch="明石",size="z1",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1b0000",face="b0003",head="aka_z1b",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000757",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「何をいまさらだ。バカも大バカ、どうしようもないバカだよ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00121",
linknext="block_00123",
},
block_00123={
{"fg",ch="明石",size="z1",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1b0000",face="b0001",head="aka_z1b",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000758",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「だから、組んだんだろ？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00122",
linknext="block_00124",
},
block_00124={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「違いない」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00123",
linknext="block_00125",
},
block_00125={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「今度会うときは冬休み明けだな」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00124",
linknext="block_00126",
},
block_00126={
{"fg",ch="明石",size="z1",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1b0000",face="b0003",head="aka_z1b",lv=4,id=9},
{"fgact",ch="明石",act="うなづく",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000759",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「うむ、そうだな。三学期だ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00125",
linknext="block_00127",
},
block_00127={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「んじゃな。明石」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00126",
linknext="block_00128",
},
block_00128={
