{"extrans",time=500},
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"俺は、亡き母に『櫻日狂想』を捧げた。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00262",
linknext="block_00264",
},
block_00264={
{"cgdel",id=-1},
{"fg",mode=-2,sync=0},
